Class Inanimated

java.lang.Object
  domain.Sprite
      domain.Inanimated
All Implemented Interfaces:
Renderable, Updatable, Collisionable, Statitzable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Scenario
public abstract class Inanimated
extends Sprite

This Specialitzation class represents a Sprite wich will never have the ability of moving. Not moving doesn't imply that the Inanimated can't set its position, change it's image, playing sounds...
